Subject: [PATCH] adcsensor: Disable io_uring build

When the adcsensor uses the io_uring lib,
That causes a reading error to LTC2497 device (an ADC/I2C
device).

This is workaround for temp solution. That will be revert after we have
a better solution with the ltc2497 driver.

Signed-off-by: Chanh Nguyen <chanh@os.amperecomputing.com>

%% original patch: 0005-Restructure-the-code-handle-PowerState-attribute.patch
---
 src/meson.build | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/meson.build b/src/meson.build
index e3e6ade..b540911 100644
--- a/src/meson.build
+++ b/src/meson.build
@@ -14,7 +14,6 @@ if get_option('adc').enabled()
             thresholds_dep,
             utils_dep,
         ],
-        cpp_args: uring_args,
         implicit_include_directories: false,
         include_directories: '../include',
         install: true,
